to be sick and ask for a leave?

84
00:04:27,087 --> 00:04:27,607
Did you forget

85
00:04:27,806 --> 00:04:29,647
that the princess of the Crimson Clan is
still on the mountain?

86
00:04:29,847 --> 00:04:30,847
