93
00:04:41,847 --> 00:04:42,607
Chong Ming,

94
00:04:42,847 --> 00:04:43,806
don't worry.

95
00:04:44,246 --> 00:04:45,967
Since I've decided
not to see her again,

96
00:04:46,207 --> 00:04:47,446
