109
00:05:08,847 --> 00:05:09,686
Why is that?

110
00:05:10,207 --> 00:05:11,727
High Priest of Grand Preceptor
knew that Shi Yu and I share

111
00:05:11,967 --> 00:05:12,886
a very deep bond.

112
00:05:14,047 --> 00:05:15,366
